summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting the redevelopment proposal of Nikkei Concerns to purchase and develop Parcel 8A-9 in the Yesler-Atlantic Neighborhood Improvement Project (Wash. R-5) area; authorizing the Director of the Department of Housing and Human Services to execute, deliver and administer a contract and deed; designating the disposition of sale proceeds; and ratifying and confirming prior actions.
committee: Health, Human Services, Education and Libraries
